channel.description:
Hello moparscape users!!!
Im writting this post,because i want to make an runescape private server. I allready,have an source and client,and i´m working on it. Im using archeron source and client. If there is someone that wants to join my team and be part of my server,contact me via this post or by skype: Gribixx If you help me developing my server,i will give you some awesome rewards when the servers is done.
My server name by now is TugaScape.
It´s 317...
Thank you all for your attention!
First post :OOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOO!!! :cool: :cool: :cool: :cool: :cool:
